      "planinhalt": "<ul>\n    <li>ISO/OSI-Referenzmodell: Netztopologien und Multiple Access Protokolle </li>\n    <li>Ethernet Physical Layer Technologien (Verkabelung, Signalisierung, Kollisionsdetektion, Repeater/Hub)</li>\n    <li>Ethernet Medium Access Control (Framestruktur, Switching, VLAN, Trunking, STP)</li>\n    <li>Wireless LAN </li>\n    <li>Internet Architektur </li>\n    <li>Netzwerk Protokolle (IPv4, IPv6), ICMP und Address Resolution Protocol (ARP) </li>\n    <li>Transport Protokolle (TCP, UDP) </li>\n    <li>Anwendungsprotokolle (HTTP, FTP, TFTP, SMTP) </li>\n    <li>Whois, Domain Name System (DNS), Dynamic Hoist Configuration Protocol (DHCP) </li>\n</ul>",
